main event: On July 7, 1968, at Eielson Air Force Base in Alaska, multiple USAF personnel reported a sighting of a bright white light that appeared to hover and then move rapidly across the sky.
interesting points: The sighting lasted approximately 23 minutes,The object was visually tracked on radar and confirmed to be in the vicinity of the base,The witnesses included members of the 354th Security Police Squadron,No sound was associated with the object during the observation,The conclusion of the investigation indicated that the object remains unidentified.
sighted object: a bright white light in the sky
witness description: USAF personnel on patrol at Eielson AFB
